node.text: Here I show you guys exactly how I load my bike into my truck without any help. With the right technique and a little practice, this can be just as easy for you! Note: not all bikes have an idle adjustment but you can install one on most of them or simply use the throttle to add a little gas on the way up the ramp. Enjoy! 😁 Brought to you by @russbrownmotorcycleattorneys #russbrownmotorcycleattorneys

❗️ＧＩＶＥＡＷＡＹ❗️

@insta360 and I are teaming up to give one of you your very own ONE X2 360 camera + a Motorcycle Mount Bundle Kit! 🥳 Every clip in this video was shot on this camera and you can see how it enables you to capture so much more than a regular camera. 🙌🏼

To enter simply complete the following:
1. Like this post ✅
2. Follow @insta360 ✅
3. Follow @smashstunts ✅
4. Tag 3 friends in the comments below ✅
 That’s it! The winner will be chosen at random and announced this Friday the 23rd at 7pm PST. 
🍀 GOOD LUCK! 🍀
**This promotion is in no way sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or associated with Instagram.**
